{
  "stem": "428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I came back home then I find out that everything is finished, that nobody is alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just know that I have a brother in [INAUDIBLE] in a-- in an ammunition factory too, yeah.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just knew over there because-- how do I-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a-- I know he is there because I-- I work with a-- with a-- with a Polish-- Polack, with a Polack, and he was working with a Polack.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to be in contact through that Polish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to write to that Polack what he was working with him and he used to the write to that Polack what I was working with him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't a Polack, it was a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I remember still the others, that Polish man that was working with my brother, it was, his name was Bielowitski, [INAUDIBLE], block 18.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Something like this, I still remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to tell you, when I was in [INAUDIBLE], in that labor camp, before that Krakow-Plaszow concentration camp, it was once, the light came out that night in the camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sabotage.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They take out the whole camp outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they put them to 10 people, every 10th out for shooting, out for shooting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "God help, I was the 10th.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they went for the police to shoot, the lights came out, the lights came back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a short and it was a win.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Someplace a wire came out from one place and came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The light went out, that's all you have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You have by the split of a second of your life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, a lot of people-- a lot of people-- I was young so I could take it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
